src: nɤ-pɤri ɯ-pɯ́-tu?
trs: Did you have dinner?

src: pɯ-tu, nɯ koʁmɯz tɤ-nɤ-pɤri-j
trs: We did, we just had dinner.' (conversation, 2016-04-12)

src: tɕiʑo ni kɤ-amɯfse-tɕi nɯ jinde kɯβdɤsqi ɯ-ro to-pa
trs: We have known each other for more than forty years.' (`More than forty years passed', 12-BzaNsa, 3)

src: tɯ-skʰrɯ mɤ-βdi tɕe nɯnɯ qartsʰaz ɯ-se ɣɯ-tsʰi mɤ-βdi ma
trs: (People say that) when one is pregnant, it is not good to drink deer blood.' (27-qartshAz, 108-109)

src: a-lɤn na-βzu
trs: He gave me an answer.' (elicited)

src: mbroχpa-skɤt kɤ-βzu ɲɯ-mkʰɤz-nɯ.
trs: They speak the nomad language (Amdo Tibetan) very well.' (140522 RdWrJAt, 129)

src: nɯnɯ qale a-tɤ-βze qʰe, iɕqʰa nɯ ɣɯ-nɯ-tsɯm qʰe,
trs: Whenever there is wind, it blows (this insect) away.' (28-kWpAz, 163)

src: kɯβde-rzɯɣ ʑo tó-wɣ-lɤt pjɤ́-wɣ-sat
trs: (The thief) killed him by cutting him into four pieces.' (140512 alibaba-zh, 115)

src: kʰa kɯ-qanɯ\redp{}nɯ ɯ-ŋgɯ zɯ, nɤkinɯ, tɯ-ɕpɤβ kɯβde-rzɯɣ tɤ-kɤ-lɤt nɯnɯ ku-sɯ-ɤlɤɣi-a cʰa-a ɕti nɤ!
trs: (not only this, but) I am (even) able to put together a corpse that had been cut into four pieces in a dark house.' (140512 alibaba-zh, 170)

src: tɯ-mɯrtsɯɣ χsɯm to-lɤt
trs: He pinched him three times.' (elicited)

src: ɯ-taʁ nɯtɕu tɯqartsɯ ʁnɯz to-lɤt
trs: He kicked two times on it.'  (150824 kelaosi-zh, 64)

src: ʁnɯ-tɯ-tʂɯβ ntsɯ cʰɯ́-wɣ-lɤt ra.
trs: It has to be sewed two times.' (12-kAtsxWb, 83)

src: a-ɣe ra ɣɯ pɤjkʰu ʑatsa <fangjia> mɯ́j-lɤt-nɯ
trs: My grandchild (and the rest of his class) are not yet on vacations.' (conversation, 2014-12-24)

src: tɯ-mɯ ka-lɤt ɯ-mpʰru nɯ tu.
trs: It is found after rain (has fallen).' (23-mbrAZim, 79)

src: qartsɯ tɕe tɕendɤre tɤjpa wuma ʑo ka-lɤt tɕe
trs: In winter, when a lot of snow has fallen,' (24-kWmu, 21)

src: tsʰɯtʰo-pɯ tɯ-rdoʁ kɯ ɯ-ku to-tɕɤt.
trs: One of the little kids stuck its head out of (the wolf's belly).' (140430 lang he qizhi xiaoshanyang-zh, 135)

src: a-ftɕɤfkɤt ci tɤ-tɕɤt tɕe jisŋi tɕʰi ʑo ɲɯ-nɤme-a pe
trs: Make me a suggestion, what should I do today?' (140515 jiesu de laoren-zh, 130)

src: a-mi ɯ-tɕʰaʁ pɯ-ɬoʁ
trs: My leg became handicapped (as a result of an accident).' (elicited)

src: aʑo kɯnɤ, a-tɕʰaʁ pjɯ-tɯ-tɕɤt ɲɯ-ŋu
trs: (Not only did you do all these crimes), you also mutilate me.' (tou dongxi de xiaohai-zh, 27)

src: tʂɤɕpʰɤt nɯnɯ ɯ-qa tú-wɣ-tɕɤt tɕe, pjɯ́-wɣ-ɣɤ-la tɕe tɯ-ɕɣa kɯ-mŋɤm phɤn tu-ti-nɯ
trs: People say that, if one digs out the plantain's root and soak it in water, it is efficient against toothache.' (12-ndZiNgri, 46-47)

src: nɯ kɤ-ndɯn lonba ɯʑo pjɯ-sɤʑe tɕe ɯ-qa cʰɯ-tɕɤt
trs: (This monk is in charge) of reading (the sûtras) from the beginning until the end.' (160721 XpWN, 44)

src: ɲɯ́-wɣ-nɤmɤle tɯ-jaʁ ku-ndɤm ʑo ɕti ma, ɯ-taʁ, ɯ-ndʑɯɣ ʑo kɯ-fse tu.
trs: When one touches it (a type of mushroom), it sticks on one's hand, as there is some kind of resin-like thing on it.' (21-kuGrummAG, 21)

src: tɕe kɯki χsɯ-ldʑa ra ɕi, kɯβde-ldʑa ra nɯnɯ, tɯʑo ɯ-kʰrɤt kú-wɣ-nɯ-ndo tɕe
trs: One has to control whether one needs three or four threads (for a given colour).' (vid-2014-04-29-092115, 76)

src: ɯ-tɯ-mɯɕtaʁ kɤ-ti kɯ [tɯ-pʰoŋbu kɤ-ndo] ʑo mɯ-pɯ-sɤ-cʰa
trs: It was so cold that one could not help shivering.' (29-RmGWzWn2, 15)

src: ju-kɯ-ɕe tɤ-ʑɣɤpa nɤ, kɯm nɯ ci la-cɯ, ci tʰa-pa nɤ, kɤ-anbaʁ ɲɯ-ŋu
trs: She pretended to go (out), she opened the door, and then closed it, and hid (inside the house).' (2003 Kunbzang, 405)

src: amaŋ, βdaʁmu, ci kɤ-pa-tɕi nɯstʰɯci ʑo tɤ-nɤrʑaʁ nɤ ri
trs: Oh, my lady, so much time has passed since we got married, but ...' (2005 Kunbzang, 414)

src: a! jinde kɤndʑi-ɣɯfsu nɯ-pa-tɕi
trs: Let us be friends!' (smanmi 2003.1, 53)

src: tɤ-tɕɯ nɯ kɯ qapi χsɯm nɯ pa-ta ndɤre, nɯ ɯ-taʁ  ndʑi-tʂʰa ka-nɯ-ta-ndʑi
trs: The boy placed the three stones (on the ground), and they made their tea on it.'  (2003 Kunbzang, 186-187)

src: zaŋ cʰo raʁ ni ʁnaʁna ʑo ʁja ku-te ɲɯ-ŋu
trs: Both copper and brass get verdigris.' (30-Com, 101)

src: nɯ rɟɤlpu kɯ\redp{}kɯ-tu nɯ pjɯ-ɕɯ-nŋam-a, nɯnɯ a-pa pjɯ-nɯ-rke-a ra
trs: I have to defeat all the kings (in the world), to subjugate them.' (150821 edu de wangzi-zh, 8)

src: nɤ-ku sɤ-rku kɯ-me
trs: (Something) that is none of your business.' (elicited)

src: tɤ-rʑaʁ kɯ-rɲɟi tu-kɯ-ŋke qʰe, tɯ-mɤpa ri cimbɤrom tu-rke ŋgrɤl.
trs: If one walks for a long time (with bad shoes), one gets blisters on one's soles.' (27-tWfCAl, 140)

src: nɤ-tsɯ ɲɯ-rnaʁ
trs: You are keeping the secret very well.' (elicited)

src: a-lu pjɤ-cɯ kʰi
trs: I lost conscience (people said).' (elicited)

src: nɯtɕu tɤ-rɤru ma sala ɲɯ-tɯ-zri ɲɯ-ŋu
trs: Get up from there, you are in the way.' (elicited)

src: ``wortɕʰi nɤ wojɤr" to-ti-nɯ tʰɯrʑi to-ʑɯ-nɯ.
trs: (The boys) asked for mercy, saying `please' one after the other.' (160704 poucet4-v2, 24-25)

src: tʰaʁ pɯ-tɕʰot-a
trs: I took a decision.' (elicited)

src: ɯʑo kɯ ta-tɯt cʰo nɤj tu-tɯ-ti nɯ tʰo ɲɯ-tʰɯɣ
trs: What he said and what you are saying match up.' (elicited)

src: ci tʰɯ-kɯ-rgɯ\redp{}rgɤz ɲɯ-ɕti tɕe, ci kɯ-xtɕɯ\redp{}xtɕi ɲɯ-ɕti tɕe, ndʑi-ŋgu mɤ-tʰon tɕe, aʑo mɤ-ɣi-a
trs: One of them is very old, the other one is very young, they are not able to take care of themselves, I will not come (to the palace and leave them behind).' (2011-05-nyima, 140)

src: aʑo βʑɯ ɕti-a ma, nɤki, pɣa maʁ-a
trs: (The bat said:) I am a mouse, not a bird.' (140427 bianfu yu huangshulang-zh, 7)

src: aʑo tɯmɯkɯmpɕi ra nɯ-tɕɯ pɯ-ŋu-a ri, [ki kɯ-fse] nɯ-aβzu-a
trs: I used to be a son of heaven, but I became like that.' (divination 2003, 30-31)

src: aʑo nɤʑo maʁ-a kɯ, a-mu mɤ-nɤmqe-a.
trs: I am not you, I will not scold my mother.' (elicited)

src: [pɯ-kɯ-cʰa] nɯ aʑo ɕti-a
trs: The one who succeeded (in doing these things) was me.' (qachGa 2003, 176)

src: stu ɯ-sɤ-dɤn nɯ [stɤmku nɯra] ŋu-nɯ. tɕe nɯra nɯ-ŋgɯ tɕe tu-ɬoʁ ŋu tɕe
trs: The place where it is most numerous is the grasslands, and it grows in these' (19-qachGa mWntoR, 24-25)

src: aʑo a-βlu ci tu
trs: I have an idea.' (150829 taishan zhi zhu-zh, 199)

src: kɯɕɯŋgɯ nɯnɯtɕu kʰɤɴqra ci pjɤ-tu.
trs: In former times, there used to be a house in ruin there.' (140522 Kamnyu zgo, 258)

src: [jɯɣmɯr kɯ-nɤpɤri] aʑo ma me-a.
trs: This evening nobody is having dinner (at home) apart from me.'   (conversation, 16-04-28)

src: kɯɕɯŋgɯ ʁzɤmi ci pjɤ-tu-ndʑi
trs: In former times, there was a husband and his wife.' (rkangrgyal 2002.2, 1)

src: ŋotɕu ɕ-pɯ-tɯ-tu-nɯ?
trs: Where (in which places) have you been?' (2003sras, 57)

src: nɤj ku-tɯ-tu ɯ́-ŋu
trs: Are you (still) alive?' (Nyima Wodzer 2003.2, 27)

src: mɯ-to-ndo-t-a,  kʰa a-ta ɕti tɕe
trs: I did not take it (with me), it is (I left it) in my home.' (150830 afanti-zh, 132)

src: a-wa ɯ-kɯr ɯ-ŋgɯ zɯ, nɯtɕu tɤ-rɣe ci a-rku tɕe
trs: In my father's mouth, there is a pearl.' (150902 hailibu-zh, 37)

src: ɯ-ku ɯ-rkɯ ri ʁɟa ʑo ɯ-mɤlɤjaʁ ra ku-ndzoʁ ɲɯ-ŋu
trs: Its legs are located (attached) next to its head.' (26-mYaRmtsaR, 49)

src: tɤ-mkɯm aro-a
trs: (Both) `I have a pillow.' (elicited)

src: rɟɤlpu nɯnɯ ɣɯ ɯ-tɕɯ sqaptɯɣ ʑo pjɤ-tu.
trs: The king had eleven sons.' (140520 ye tiane-zh, 4)

src: tu-βze-a kɤ-cʰa nɯra lonba ʑo nɤʑɯɣ tɤ-ɣɤ-tu-t-a ɕti tɕe
trs: I endowed you with all the things I could make.' (140425 shizi puluomixiusi he daxiang-zh, 16)

src: [nɯɕɯŋgɯ ɣɯ ɯ-\textbf{laχtɕʰa} pɯ-kɯ-tu] nɯra ɕ-tú-wɣ-sɯ-rtoʁ tɕe,
trs: They go (there) and show (the child$_i$) [objects that he$_i$ used to have before] (in his$_i$ previous life, when he$_i$ was a lama).' (160722 skWBli, 6)

src: [\textbf{jla} nɯ-ʁrɯ kɯ-tu] ra kɯnɤ, nɯ-rpaʁ kɯ ɲɯ-z-rɤɕi-nɯ pɯ-ŋu tɕe,
trs: Even the hybrid yaks that had horns used to pull (the plough) with their shoulders (rather than with their horns).' (25-stuxsi, 21-22)

src: ɯ-ru nɯnɯ, kɯ-mpɕɯ\redp{}mpɕu ʑo ŋu, [ɯ-mdzu ri kɯ-tu] me
trs: Its stalk, it is very smooth, and it does not have any thorns.' (11-qrontshom, 42)

src: nɯtɕu ɕe-a ŋu
trs: (For all these reasons) I am going there.' (2011-04-smanmi, 46)

src: tɯ\redp{}tɤ-tɯ-nɤma-t rcanɯ, pe ntsɯ ɕti
trs: Everything that you do is always good.' (150822 laoye zuoshi zongshi duide-zh, 252)

src: tú-wɣ-ɕtʂo ŋu ma tú-wɣ-skɤr maʁ
trs: One measures (the quantity to be used) by scooping, not by weighing.' (31-cha, 12)

src: ɲɯ-ɣɤkʰɯ ndʐa ɕti wo ma, tɕe a-mɲaʁ ɲɯ-ɕɯ-mŋɤm ndʐa ɕti ma, ɲɯ-ɣɤwu-a maʁ
trs: (The reason why I shed tears) is because it is smoky, and it hurts my eyes, it is not that I am crying.' (qaCpa 202, 95)

src: tɕetʰa nɤʑo tɯ-si ɕti
trs: (Otherwise) you will (certainly) die.' (2011-04-smanmi, 70)

src: `ɯ-kɤrme tɯ-ldʑa a-mɤ-jɤ-tɯ-ɣɯt ra' tɤ-tɯt-a maʁ ɯ́-ŋu
trs: Didn't I say: `Do not bring back anything, not even a hair (from her head).'' (2014-kWlAG., 691)

src: \textbf{nɤʑo} nɤ-tɯ-ci ɕ-tɤ-tɯ-nɯ-ru-t ɯ́-ŋu?
trs: Was it for yourself that you brought the water?

imtwordshtml: tral-aor-auto-bring-pst:tr-1sg
src: \textbf{aʑo} ɕ-tɤ-nɯ-ru-t-a ŋu
trs: I brought it for myself.

src: tɕeri, ɯ-pi mɯ-pjɤ-rɤʑi qʰendɤre,  \textbf{ɯ-ɬaʁ} \textbf{nɯ} pjɤ-rɤʑi ɕti qʰe
trs: But his elder brother was not there, it was his brother's wife who was there.' (140512 alibaba, 62)

src: kɯki tɕʰeme ki ndɤre aʑɯɣ a-pɯ-ŋu tʂaŋ ma tɕe \textbf{aʑo} pɯ-nɯ-mto-t-a ɕti tɕe
trs: This girl, it would be fair if she were mine, as it was I who found her.' (140517 buaishuohua, 102)

src: aʑo \textbf{pɤnmawombɤr} tu-ti-a ɕti ma, \textbf{nɤj} ɲɯ-ta-nɯ-ɤkʰɤzŋga maʁ
trs: I am saying ``Padma 'Od 'bar", it is not you that I am calling.' (2012 Norbzang, 163)

src: kʰɯɣɲɟɯ ri pɣɤtɕɯ ni ɲɯ-ɤnɯɣro-ndʑi tɕe, \textbf{nɯ} ɲɯ-nɤre-a ɕti wo
trs: On the window two birds were playing, this is what I was laughing about.' (2014-kWlAG, 396)

src: \textbf{nɯ} \textbf{ɯ-ndʐa} \textbf{kɯ} nɯ-si ʁo pɯ-maʁ.
trs: It was not because of this that shed died.' (150907 srWn, 23)

src: [\textbf{xɕiri} \textbf{nɯ} \textbf{kɯ} qapri bɯxsi pjɤ-sat kɯ-ŋu] nɯnɯ ko-tso
trs: He realized that it was the weasel that had killed the python.' (140518 xuezhe he huangshulang-zh, 34)

src: aʑo rŋgɯ ɕti-a qhe, rŋɯl ste-a me qhe, nɤʑo nɤ-ŋgra a-pɯ-ŋu tɕe tɤ-nɯ-ndɤm
trs: I am a boulder, I have no use of (this) silver, may this be your reward (for helping me), take it.' (divination, 98)

src: tɕe jinde aj pɯ-mto-t-a me ri, pɯ-kɯ-xtɕi tɕe pɯ́-wɣ-mto
trs: These days I have not seen any (crane), but I did see (some) when I was young.' (22-qomndroN, 25)

src: tɕe ʑara nɯ-kɤ-nɯ-ndza tɕe koŋla ji-nɯ maŋe woma
trs: They don't  plant any (maize) for themselves to eat, (they plant it to feed their pigs).'  (140522 kAmYW tWji, 68)

src: tɯ-ci ɯ-rkɯ zɯ ku-rɤʑi-a tɕe nɯre ri ku-nɯ-tsʰi-a ɕti ma ɯ-ŋgɯ ri kɤ-ari-a me, ɕ-tu-nɤŋkɯŋke-a ri me
trs: I am staying near the water and drinking (water) there, I did not go into the water at all, I am not walking around in it.' (aesop lang he yang 16-17)

src: nɯŋa ɯ-ndza sna ma nɯ ma sna me
trs: (Oat) is good as fodder for cattle, but apart from that it is not good for anything.' (08-qaJAGi, 8)

imt: \textsc{1sg} \textsc{interj} also \textsc{tral}-\textsc{aor}-\textsc{auto}-say[II]-\textsc{1sg} \textsc{sbj}:\textsc{pcp}-exist not.exist:\textsc{fact} \textsc{lnk} \textsc{1sg} \textsc{advers} \textsc{ipfv}-become-\textsc{1sg} also \textsc{sbj}:\textsc{pcp}-be.needed not.exist:\textsc{fact} \textsc{lnk} \textsc{2sg}.\textsc{poss}-\textsc{emph}\redp{}together.with \textsc{emph} come:\textsc{fact}-\textsc{1sg} be:\textsc{fact} \textsc{lnk} \textsc{dem} apart.from \textsc{1sg}:\textsc{gen} \textsc{sbj}:\textsc{pcp}-be.needed \textsc{sbj}:\textsc{pcp}-exist not.exist:\textsc{fact}
src: [[aʑo joβ tɕi ɕ-tɤ-nɯ-tɯt-a] kɯ-tu] me qʰe  [aʑo ndɤre ɲɯ-ɤβzu-a ri kɯ-ra] me qʰe, nɤ-rcɯ\redp{}rca ʑo ɣi-a ŋu ma nɯ ma [[aʑɯɣ kɯ-ra] kɯ-tu] me
trs: I did not go and heed (the girl who was calling us), and I don't need to become anything special, I don't need anything, apart from following you.' (2003 kandZislama, 36-38)

src: kɯ-ŋɤn mɤ-nɤma-ndʑi maka me
trs: There is no evil thing that they do not do/They do all kinds of evil things.' (140428 yonggan de xiaocaifeng-zh, 175)

src: nɯ kɯ-fse ci tɯ-ŋu, nɯ mɤ-kɯ-naχtɕɯɣ ci \textbf{tɯ-ŋu} \textbf{tɯ-ŋu}
trs: You are (someone) like that, you are different (from normal people).' (2011-04-smanmi, 47)

src: ki aʑo a-jaʁ ki jamar ɣɤʑu.
trs: The wild yak horn is about as big as my hand here.' (20-RmbroN, 28)
